# sr_ru_proxy.list
# Services to route through PROXY.
# Format: Shadowrocket RULE-SET entries without policy column.
# Used by: RULE-SET,.../sr_ru_proxy.list,PROXY
# Updated: 2026-04-27, based on Brawl Stars working GLOBAL PROXY log.
# IMPORTANT: tun-included-routes is intentionally not used in this profile.
# IMPORTANT: broad experimental cloud ranges 44.240.0.0/15 and 52.32.0.0/15 were removed.

# Telegram domains and web resources
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,t.me
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,telegram.org
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,telegram.me
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,telegram.dog
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,telesco.pe
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,telegra.ph
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,legra.ph
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,graph.org
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,comments.app
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,contest.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,telegram-cdn.org
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,cdn-telegram.org
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,telegramdownload.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,tdesktop.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,tg.dev
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,tx.me
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,telegram.space
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,telega.one
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,telegram
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,nicegram

